title: Starts of the Week + Week 11 Breakdown, Goose Burns - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/18
description:
It’s football time! Week 11 is here and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason dive into Week 11 matchups and reveal their Starts of the Week! Plus, injury updates, and a new edition of “Never Not Working!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 18th, 2021.
  
 (04:55) - Never Not Working
 (11:45) - NFL News
 (24:00) - Fantasy Forecast
 (24:20) - Colts at Bills
 (29:00) - Ravens at Bears
 (33:50) - Lions at Browns
 (39:10) - Texans at Titans
 (44:20) - Packers at Vikings
 (49:25) - Dolphins at Jets
 (54:05) - Saints at Eagles
 (57:40) - Starts of the Week
 (57:50) - QB Starts of the Week 
 (01:00:50) - RB Starts of the Week 
 (01:03:00) - WR Starts of the Week
 (01:05:10) - TE Starts of the Week
 (01:07:40) - Boom Boom Kicker of the Week
